description:
Asghan: The Dragon Slayer is a fantasy-themed hack-and-slash action role-playing computer game developed by Silmarils and released in December 1998. Players take on the persona of Asghan, a warrior prince who swears to avenge the death of his father by dragons. The game is praised for smooth integration of action and role-playing elements as well as a wide array of enemies and weapons. It suffers, however, from lacking character development and awkward controls.


Game disc music is included as .mp3 under the folder - &quot;asghan music ripper&quot;
No-CD crack is included under - &quot;bb_asghan.zip&quot;

This game does work, but not on Win7(or anything newer than Win-XP)
The solution is to use a virtual machine with an older operating system installed(or just an old computer with WinXP will work)



1- download VM-Ware player &lt;a href=&quot;
https://my.vmware.com/web/vmware/free#desktop_end_user_computing/vmware_player/6_0&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
https://my.vmware.com/web/vmware/free#desktop_end_user_computing/vmware_player/6_0&lt;/a&gt;
It's very user friendly.

2- download some older windows OS(if you have a winXP disc in hand, then just use that). I prefer TinyXP since it uses very little resources. &lt;a href=&quot;
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/5388565/Windows_Tiny_XP_Rev10-eXPerience&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/5388565/Windows_Tiny_XP_Rev10-eXPerience&lt;/a&gt;

3- Create a new virtual machine using VMWare-player, give it the tinxp.iso you download from above and follow installation instructions to get that onto your Virtual machine.

4- Get Asghan onto the virtual machine. A USB flash-drive works easy, just copy asghan to the USB-stick, unplug the USB-stick. Click somewhere within the virtual machine and only then plug back the USB-stick into your physical computer. Now your tinyXP virtual machine should be able to see the USB-stick. Copy asghan from that onto virtual machine.

5- Extract all the files from &quot;bb_asghan.zip&quot; to the main asghan folder(the one containing _start.exe). Replace all files with the cracked versions.

6- Run _start.exe and enjoy!




If the game fails to run, tinker with compatibility settings of _start.exe
try using the original _start.exe (the uncracked version).

...and if anyone gets this to work on Win7/8, let me know please
